<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Payment Confirmation</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #0c4da2;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header img {
      max-width: 200px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #0c4da2;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .details {
      background-color: white;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .details table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }
    .details td {
      padding: 8px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
    }
    .details td:first-child {
      font-weight: bold;
      width: 40%;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="https://metabolixmd.com/logo.png" alt="MetabolixMD Logo">
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Payment Confirmation</h2>
      <p>Dear <%= name %>,</p>
      <p>Thank you for your payment. We're pleased to confirm that your payment has been successfully processed.</p>
      
      <div class="details">
        <table>
          <tr>
            <td>Order ID:</td>
            <td><%= orderId %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Amount Paid:</td>
            <td>$<%= amount.toFixed(2) %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Payment Date:</td>
            <td><%= date %></td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </div>
      
      <p>Your order is now being processed. You can track your order status in your account dashboard.</p>
      
      <a href="https://metabolixmd.com/profile-details" class="button">View Order Details</a>
      
      <p>If you have any questions about your order, please don't hesitate to contact our customer support team.</p>
      
      <p>Thank you for choosing MetabolixMD!</p>
      
      <p>Best regards,<br>The MetabolixMD Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> MetabolixMD. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>This email was sent to you because you made a purchase on our website.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>